data.description: **SELLERS ARE OFFERING a $5,000 Credit towards Closing, AND a 1 Year Home Warranty**  Welcome to your dream home! This charming 3-bedroom, 1.5-bathroom Brick Rancher is nestled in one of the most desirable areas in Frederick County, offering a perfect blend of comfort and convenience. As you enter the home you will come across the spacious living room that provides an ideal space for relaxation and entertaining, boasting plenty of natural light that enhances the welcoming ambiance, and a Brick fireplace that is perfect on your cold winter nights! The heart of the home is the well-appointed kitchen, featuring modern appliances and ample counter space for culinary enthusiasts. The three bedrooms offer a cozy and plenty of room for the Family. Oh, let’s not forget.. you have a main floor Washer and Dryer. (No more going to the basement to do your Laundry) Do you like spending your time outside? This home offers a large spacious backyard that is fully fenced in, and is great for hosting your backyard BBQ’s… or parties. Are you a Car enthusiast?? **This property features a large shop that is perfect for working on all of the projects your significant other told you not to buy, but you decided to buy anyway… yeah, plenty of space…. Don't miss the opportunity to make this Brick Rancher your forever home. Schedule a viewing today and experience the perfect blend of comfort, style, and convenience in one of the most desirable areas in Frederick County. Your dream home awaits!
